  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/85203c86763e1d05dda8c07644ee288d.poster.avif?t=1717124525\" width=604 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/85203c86763e1d05dda8c07644ee288d.webm?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/85203c86763e1d05dda8c07644ee288d.mp4?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This Side Up is a puzzle-platform game that blurs the lines between player and platform. Run, jump, and grab with four characters who fall in different directions. Get each player and box to its destination to beat the level. And remember, you're on company time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/894d3d131eb7347dc66b61d10e7452da.poster.avif?t=1717124525\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/894d3d131eb7347dc66b61d10e7452da.webm?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/894d3d131eb7347dc66b61d10e7452da.mp4?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/cf43c07c130cfd469e767bc8c1d60f4a.poster.avif?t=1717124525\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/cf43c07c130cfd469e767bc8c1d60f4a.webm?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617930/extras/cf43c07c130cfd469e767bc8c1d60f4a.mp4?t=1717124525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game includes 50 levels and hours of mind-bending puzzles with an array of platforms and items. Each level is hand-crafted and shows you something new and interesting about the game world.",
